{
  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Resolve Missing Translation Keys for Schedule View\n\nFix missing translation keys in schedule.html that are preventing proper text display in the schedule interface. All keys with the 'schedule_' prefix need to be properly defined and integrated.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify all 'schedule_' translation keys referenced in schedule.html\n- Check which keys are missing from translation files (e.g., en.json, i18n files)\n- Add missing translation key definitions with appropriate text values\n- Verify keys exist for all supported languages in the application\n- Ensure proper fallback behavior if translations are unavailable\n- Test schedule.html to confirm all text displays correctly without missing key warnings\n\nEdge Cases to Consider:\n- Keys that may be dynamically constructed or computed\n- Nested translation key structures\n- Plural forms or parameterized translations for schedule-related text",
